data.description: PROFESsIONAL PHOTOS COMING SOON!  Why wait to built when you have this ''Like New''  stunning 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home in the gated 55+ community of Bridgewater in Viera. This beautifully updated home was built in 2020 and has just under 1600sf of living space.  In the kitchen you'll find plenty of space in the 42 inch cabinets.  Quartz counter tops and stainless steel appliances.  Tile flooring throughout the entire home!  Eight foot doorways.  Large master bedroom.  Master bath has a double sink with marble top and a large glass enclosed walk-in shower.  Spacious guest bedrooms.  Over $40,000 in updates have went into this home with great detail. Screened in patio overlooking the lake. Open floor plan.  Corner lot!  Accordion shutters on all windows.  This home is absolutely gorgeous.   Come take a  look today.
